# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:48
translate spanish hwb_s13_f4d341ee:

    # "The solemn loneliness of the open road extends far past my headlights and into the dark."
    "La solemne soledad del camino abierto se extiende más allá de mis faros y se adentra en la oscuridad."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:50
translate spanish hwb_s13_24cdc618:

    # "A cool wind breezes through the cracked window and tosses around our hair as a jazzy experimental track crackles through the speakers. With each horn screech, Marina sinks further into her seat."
    "Un viento fresco se cuela por la ventana entreabierta y revuelve nuestro cabello mientras una canción experimental de jazz crepita por los altavoces. Con cada chirrido de trompeta, Marina se hunde más en su asiento."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:52
translate spanish hwb_s13_adfce917:

    # "She looks miserable."
    "Se ve miserable."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:54
translate spanish hwb_s13_75a9aa94:

    # Amber "Do you want me to turn down the music a little?"
    Amber "Если хочешь, я могу сделать музыку немного тише."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:56
translate spanish hwb_s13_6cdc936a:

    # Marina "Oh no, I’m fine. It’s not bothering me."
    Marina "О, нет, все в порядке. Она меня не беспокоит."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:58
translate spanish hwb_s13_b2b31fe0:

    # "She tries to disguise the glint of agony in her eyes by speaking in her usual peppy tone, but the pain still seeps through the cracks in her voice."
    "Intenta disimular el destello de agonía en sus ojos hablando con su tono habitual y animado, pero el dolor aún se filtra por las grietas de su voz."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:60
translate spanish hwb_s13_d07e2b62:

    # "A hollowness anchors down my chest. I don’t try burying it. The last time someone told me everything was fine I ended up losing them. Maybe I’m just paranoid, but I don’t want to risk it."
    "Un vacío ancla mi pecho. No intento enterrarlo. La última vez que alguien me dijo que todo estaba bien, terminé perdiéndolo. Tal vez solo soy paranoica, pero no quiero arriesgarme."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:64
translate spanish hwb_s13_5393ee46:

    # Amber "Seriously, are you okay?"
    Amber "Я серьезно, ты в порядке?"

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:66
translate spanish hwb_s13_f558d383:

    # Marina "No, really! I’m fi—"
    Marina "Да! Я действительно в пор..."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:70
translate spanish hwb_s13_98a010d6:

    # Amber "Don’t lie to me."
    Amber "Не ври мне"

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:72
translate spanish hwb_s13_d40bd359:

    # "My sharpness takes her off guard and she shifts her gaze. But I don’t care. This could be urgent."
    "Mi brusquedad la toma por sorpresa y desvía la mirada. Pero no me importa. Esto podría ser urgente."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:74
translate spanish hwb_s13_e6dd7b04:

    # "Sighing, she hangs her head."
    "Suspirando, baja la cabeza."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:76
translate spanish hwb_s13_4d4f48b3:

    # Marina "Well…"
    Marina "Ну…"

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:78
translate spanish hwb_s13_343b94ea:

    # Amber "Yeah?"
    Amber "Ага?"

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:82
translate spanish hwb_s13_a807261a:

    # Marina "I kind of need to…"
    Marina "Ну мне очень надо…"

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:84
translate spanish hwb_s13_52165b98:

    # "Her voice trails off into a pit. Regret and shame color her face, as if she’s brought great shame to her household or something equally dumb."
    "Su voz se desvanece en un pozo. El arrepentimiento y la vergüenza colorean su rostro, como si hubiera traído una gran deshonra a su hogar o algo igualmente tonto."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:86
translate spanish hwb_s13_052c7db1:

    # "My voice voice grows tense—urgent, my driving sloppy. Every pore of my clammy palms is stuck to the wheel. The hollowness comes back."
    "Mi voz se vuelve tensa—urgente, mi conducción descuidada. Cada poro de mis palmas sudorosas está pegado al volante. El vacío regresa."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:90
translate spanish hwb_s13_1b1db5e0:

    # Amber "Marina, what is it?"
    Amber "Марина, что такое?"

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:94
translate spanish hwb_s13_1d901600:

    # Marina "I kind of need to, you know…"
    Marina "Ну мне вроде как надо... Ну ты знаешь..."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:96
translate spanish hwb_s13_5c011b0a:

    # "Marina winces, her mouth stretching into a pallid grimace. She clutches at her stomach and groans."
    "Marina se encoge, su boca se estira en una mueca pálida. Se agarra el estómago y gime."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:102
translate spanish hwb_s13_2db3d17e:

    # "You’re kidding."
    "Estás bromeando."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:104
translate spanish hwb_s13_8a865856:

    # "I slap my hand against my forehead."
    "Me golpeo la frente con la mano."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:106
translate spanish hwb_s13_68294917:

    # "How many more times am I going to let myself get worked up over something so stupid?"
    "¿Cuántas veces más voy a dejarme alterar por algo tan estúpido?"

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:110
translate spanish hwb_s13_eca36cb4:

    # Amber "What did I tell you about that burrito?"
    Amber "Ну и что я говорила тебе про это буррито?"

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:112
translate spanish hwb_s13_fa429c06:

    # Marina "I know! But I was so hungry!"
    Marina "Я знаю! Но мне так хотелось кууушать..."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:114
translate spanish hwb_s13_b7922ea3:

    # Amber "You never trust gas station burritos, Mare! That’s one of the first rules of the road."
    Amber "Никогда не доверяй заправочным буррито, Мари! Это одно из первых правил на дороге."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:116
translate spanish hwb_s13_2a7e1f49:

    # Marina "I didn’t think it would end up like this! I didn’t knooow!"
    Marina "Я не думало, что оно все так выйдет! Я не знаааааалаа..."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:118
translate spanish hwb_s13_c89e8df7:

    # "A flood is starting to form in her eyes. Whether it’s because of pain or my scolding, I’m not sure."
    "Un diluvio empieza a formarse en sus ojos. No estoy segura si es por el dolor o por mi regaño."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:120
translate spanish hwb_s13_ec49a638:

    # "Hopefully it’s both and she takes this opportunity to learn something."
    "Ojalá que sea por ambas y que aproveche esta oportunidad para aprender algo."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:124
translate spanish hwb_s13_40ad2bd5:

    # Amber "Well, you’re gonna have to deal with it for now. The septic tank needs to be drained and I can’t do that until we get to Arches."
    Amber "Ну, тебе придется потерпеть. Биотуалет нужно прочистить, а я не смогу этого сделать, пока мы не доберемся до парка Арчес."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:128
translate spanish hwb_s13_30c6b122:

    # Marina "Wh-What?"
    Marina "Ч-что?"

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:132
translate spanish hwb_s13_4daedb16:

    # "Despair sets in and the hopelessness of the situation dawns on her."
    "La desesperación se instala y la inutilidad de la situación le cae encima."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:134
translate spanish hwb_s13_ccfa0e80:

    # Amber "I’ll stop if we pass a gas station or something, but that’s not gonna be for a while."
    Amber "Я остановлюсь, если мы будем проезжать заправку или что-то типа того, но в ближайшее время этого не случится."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:136
translate spanish hwb_s13_8d5efe18:

    # "Despair turns into desperation. Marina frantically looks for something to latch onto, anything to help reclaim her hope."
    "La desesperación se convierte en desesperación. Marina busca frenéticamente algo a lo que aferrarse, cualquier cosa que la ayude a recuperar su esperanza."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:140
translate spanish hwb_s13_2d51497d:

    # Marina "What about a rest stop?"
    Marina "А как на счет остановки в месте для отдыха?"

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:144
translate spanish hwb_s13_590c4165:

    # Amber "You serious?"
    Amber "Серьезно?"

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:148
translate spanish hwb_s13_9b331693:

    # Marina "Sure, why not? I saw a sign for one down the road. Should be coming up pretty quick."
    Marina "Конечно, почему нет? Я видела знак на дороге, что тут совсем недалеко."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:154
translate spanish hwb_s13_8dfee97e:

    # Amber "Hah {w=0.1}hah{w=0.9}—no."
    Amber "Ха {w=0.1}ха{w=0.9}—нет."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:158
translate spanish hwb_s13_27bf0f1b:

    # Marina "What? And why not?"
    Marina "Что? Почему нет?"

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:162
translate spanish hwb_s13_e81ce848:

    # Amber "Because you’re better than that."
    Amber "Потому что ты выше этого."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:166
translate spanish hwb_s13_9f1a9475:

    # Marina "No I’m not, I swear! Please, I really gotta go!"
    Marina "Нет, я не выше! Пожалуйста, мне очень нужно!"

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:168
translate spanish hwb_s13_3f92ae33:

    # Amber "Rest stops aren’t for people like us. They’re for people like Mariah."
    Amber "Места для отдыха не для таких как мы. Они для людей вроде Марии."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:170
translate spanish hwb_s13_5de021fa:

    # Amber "Only the scum of the earth use them."
    Amber "Только отбросы пользуются ими."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:172
translate spanish hwb_s13_a9390f2f:

    # "At least, that’s what Gramps used to say."
    "Al menos, eso es lo que solía decir el abuelo."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:174
translate spanish hwb_s13_3f9e7fcd:

    # "I’ve never actually been to one, mostly because he refused to use them. But if a people-loving hippie like Gramps referred to them as ‘cesspools of villainy, where the seedy underbelly of humanity flocks,' then I’m not sure I want to."
    "Nunca he estado en una, principalmente porque él se negaba a usarlas. Pero si un hippie amante de la gente como el abuelo las llamaba \"pozos de villanía, donde se congrega el sórdido inframundo de la humanidad\", entonces no estoy segura de querer hacerlo."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:178
translate spanish hwb_s13_a13e128c:

    # Marina "Amber."
    Marina "Эмбер."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:180
translate spanish hwb_s13_8937d9da:

    # "Her voice deepens, straining as she enunciates every single word ."
    "Su voz se vuelve más grave, esforzándose mientras pronuncia cada palabra."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:184
translate spanish hwb_s13_ebba55f3:

    # Marina "I don’t care if it makes me scum. If we don’t stop now, I am going to explode."
    Marina "Мне все равно, если это сделает меня отбросом. Если мы не остановимся - меня прорвет."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:186
translate spanish hwb_s13_f4a420e7:

    # "I wave her off, but before I can counterattack she dives in an inch from my face."
    "La despido con la mano, pero antes de que pueda contraatacar, se acerca a una pulgada de mi cara."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:191
translate spanish hwb_s13_19b25bb8:

    # Marina "{size=+12}EXPLODE, AMBER!{/size}" with hpunch
    Marina "{size=+12}ХВАТИТ, ЭМБЕР!{/size}" with hpunch

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:193
translate spanish hwb_s13_e01e6efb:

    # Marina "We {i}are{/i} going to that rest stop, whether you like it or not. Do you hear me?"
    Marina "{i}Мы{/i} едем на эту остановку для отдыха, нравится тебе это или нет, понятно?"

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:195
translate spanish hwb_s13_70745886:

    # "I gulp and reply with a shaky nod as Marina looks on with crazed eyes."
    "Trago saliva y respondo con un asentimiento tembloroso mientras Marina me mira con ojos enloquecidos."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:197
translate spanish hwb_s13_43843cbf:

    # "I never knew she could be so scary."
    "Nunca supe que podía ser tan aterradora."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:201
translate spanish hwb_s13_901d61a1:

    # "She backs off and the usual pluck in her voice returns, flipping from sour to sweet in an instant."
    "Se retira y la vivacidad habitual regresa a su voz, cambiando de agria a dulce en un instante."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:203
translate spanish hwb_s13_d60c2ad9:

    # Marina "Thank {cps=8}yoooou.{/cps}"
    Marina "{cps=8} Спасиииибо.{/cps}"

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:207
translate spanish hwb_s13_981a148c:

    # "Defeated and mildly disturbed, I jitter my eyes back and forth and wait for the exit."
    "Derrotada y ligeramente perturbada, muevo los ojos de un lado a otro y espero la salida."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:209
translate spanish hwb_s13_83e889c8:

    # "Who knows? Maybe it won’t be so bad.. Wouldn’t be the first time Gramps over-exaggerated. I’m ninety percent sure he was wrong about the government introducing the plague to local cat populations."
    "¿Quién sabe? Tal vez no sea tan malo... No sería la primera vez que el abuelo exagera. Estoy noventa por ciento segura de que se equivocó sobre el gobierno introduciendo la plaga en las poblaciones de gatos locales."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:211
translate spanish hwb_s13_674a8bfe:

    # "I pull over to an isolated exit ramp, which trails off into a dark lot."
    "Me detengo en una rampa de salida aislada, que se desvía hacia un estacionamiento oscuro."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:213
translate spanish hwb_s13_99874377:

    # "The lonely island is lit only by the sharp, unnatural light emanating from a shack on the edge of the lot, never treading more than a short distance from the building, denying its surrounding even the comfort of a dim glow."
    "La isla solitaria está iluminada solo por la luz aguda y antinatural que emana de una choza en el borde del lote, sin extenderse más allá de una corta distancia del edificio, negándole a sus alrededores incluso el consuelo de un tenue resplandor."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:215
translate spanish hwb_s13_8118502c:

    # "Despite the eerie darkness, we’re not alone. A lone big-rig with a half-assed parking job hulks over the lot."
    "A pesar de la oscuridad inquietante, no estamos solas. Un camión de carga solitario, mal estacionado, se cierne sobre el lote."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:217
translate spanish hwb_s13_942e56d1:

    # "Must have been in a rush."
    "Debe haber tenido prisa."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:219
translate spanish hwb_s13_137014cf:

    # "Rolling my eyes, I squeeze into a parking space that isn’t being hogged by the trailer."
    "Poniendo los ojos en blanco, me meto en un espacio de estacionamiento que no está acaparado por el remolque."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:223
translate spanish hwb_s13_d818d30e:

    # "I cut the ignition, and in the ensuing silence, scan the shadowed area for anything unusual."
    "Apago el motor, y en el silencio que sigue, escaneo el área sombreada en busca de algo inusual."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:227
translate spanish hwb_s13_ad32b720:

    # "As I watch, a silhouette emerges from a door, framed by the light from within."
    "Mientras observo, una silueta emerge de una puerta, enmarcada por la luz del interior."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:235
translate spanish hwb_s13_cc6b5304:

    # "But before I can warn her, Marina springs from the motorhome to run for the shack."
    "Pero antes de que pueda advertirle, Marina salta de la casa rodante para correr hacia la choza."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:239
translate spanish hwb_s13_4aa015f2:

    # Amber "Hey, wait! It’s not safe!"
    Amber "Эй, погоди! Это небезопасно!"

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:243
translate spanish hwb_s13_ce91eb70:

    # "Without pulling the key from the dash, I launch out the door and after Marina."
    "Sin sacar la llave del tablero, salgo disparada por la puerta y tras Marina."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:289
translate spanish hwb_s13_c908814d:

    # "Why the hell do we always end up running?"
    "¿Por qué demonios siempre terminamos corriendo?"

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:291
translate spanish hwb_s13_d4fd5263:

    # "The figure towers in the entranceway."
    "La figura se yergue en la entrada."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:293
translate spanish hwb_s13_d5323ba6:

    # "Kicking up gravel, I screech to a standstill right behind Marina."
    "Levantando gravilla, freno en seco justo detrás de Marina."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:295
translate spanish hwb_s13_c9a90596:

    # "Marina keeps jogging in place, unable to distract herself from the inevitable any other way."
    "Marina sigue trotando en el mismo lugar, sin poder distraerse de lo inevitable de otra manera."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:306
translate spanish hwb_s13_6d76a7ee:

    # "As my eyes adjust, his features materialize. He stares at us for an uncomfortable period of time, the bill of his unwashed baseball cap masking his eyebrows, making his stoic expression even harder to read."
    "Mientras mis ojos se ajustan, sus rasgos se materializan. Nos mira fijamente durante un período incómodo de tiempo, la visera de su gorra de béisbol sucia oculta sus cejas, haciendo que su expresión estoica sea aún más difícil de leer."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:308
translate spanish hwb_s13_b79aa927:

    # Trucker "The woman’s bathroom is closed."
    Trucker "Женский сортир закрыт."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:310
translate spanish hwb_s13_220f9da9:

    # "He points to a paper taped to the door, the words ‘out of order’ scribbled in marker."
    "Señala un papel pegado en la puerta, con las palabras 'fuera de servicio' garabateadas en marcador."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:316
translate spanish hwb_s13_e0843a92:

    # Trucker "I checked."
    Trucker "Я проверил."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:321
translate spanish hwb_s13_f772e7cf:

    # "His scratchy voice rings with a slight twang. Dried food stains sit splattered on his tank top, his flannel unable to conceal the ripe stench."
    "Su voz rasposa resuena con un ligero acento. Manchas de comida seca salpican su camiseta sin mangas, y su camisa de franela no logra ocultar el hedor rancio."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:323
translate spanish hwb_s13_074d3b0d:

    # "I have to force myself to not look away."
    "Tengo que obligarme a no apartar la mirada."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:328
translate spanish hwb_s13_b43a7b1e:

    # Marina "I can’t hold it anymore! What do we do what do we do what do we do what do we dooooo?"
    Marina "Я не могу больше терпеть! Что нам делать, что же делать, что делать, что делать нам, чтооо нам делааааааать?"

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:332
translate spanish hwb_s13_ebca7bd7:

    # Amber "Relax. Just use the guys’ bathroom."
    Amber "Успокойся. Просто используй мужской туалет."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:334
translate spanish hwb_s13_8495e293:

    # Marina "Wh-What? Is that even legal?"
    Marina "Ч-что? Это вообще законно?"

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:338
translate spanish hwb_s13_71fd51a8:

    # Amber "There's probably a North Carolina joke somewhere in there."
    Amber "Похоже на шутку из Северной Каролины."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:343
translate spanish hwb_s13_5d7397f4:

    # Amber "Dunno. Probably. Just use it, I’ll keep watch."
    Amber "Не знаю. Скорее всего. Просто используй его, я буду следить за входом."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:345
translate spanish hwb_s13_e58f6700:

    # "The man interjects, his eyes still fixated on us."
    "El hombre interrumpe, con los ojos aún fijos en nosotras."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:349
translate spanish hwb_s13_f2982e6e:

    # Trucker "Don’t worry. I wasn’t too bad this time. It should be cleared out."
    Trucker "Не переживайте, в этот раз у меня все было не так уж и плохо. Сортир, наверное, даже подчистили."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:353
translate spanish hwb_s13_208cb5d1:

    # "A disgusted groan slips out of me. I’m going to pretend I didn’t hear that."
    "Un gemido de asco se me escapa. Voy a fingir que no escuché eso."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:357
translate spanish hwb_s13_f4a5d2d8:

    # Marina "Well, if you say so…"
    Marina "Ну, если ты так говоришь…"

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:369
translate spanish hwb_s13_b319d046:

    # "Without a second of hesitation, Marina races past the man and into the restroom."
    "Sin un segundo de duda, Marina pasa corriendo al lado del hombre y entra al baño."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:371
translate spanish hwb_s13_aeb094ac:

    # "Her voice echoes from within."
    "Su voz resuena desde adentro."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:373
translate spanish hwb_s13_546aac0c:

    # Marina "WHOA! IS THIS A TROUGH? I THOUGHT THEY WERE JUST A MYTH!"
    Marina "ООО! ЭТО ДЫРА В ПОЛУ? Я ТО ДУМАЛА, ЧТО ЭТО ТАКОЙ МИФ!"

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:377
translate spanish hwb_s13_e38515c7:

    # "I look at the man and shrug while awkwardly laughing off Marina’s comment."
    "Miro al hombre y me encojo de hombros mientras me río torpemente para disimular el comentario de Marina."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:381
translate spanish hwb_s13_606b7bb6:

    # "Why is he still here?"
    "¿Por qué sigue aquí?"

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:385
translate spanish hwb_s13_b0c98293:

    # Amber "So, uh, is that your truck?"
    Amber "Так значит... это твой грузовик?"

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:389
translate spanish hwb_s13_23677106:

    # "His serious expression morphs into a wide grin, showing off his sickly, yellow teeth, each about as cracked and decaying as the walls."
    "Su expresión seria se transforma en una amplia sonrisa, mostrando sus dientes amarillos y enfermizos, cada uno tan agrietado y deteriorado como las paredes."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:391
translate spanish hwb_s13_45b04d6c:

    # "Wiping his nose with the back of his hand, he leans up against an old soda machine."
    "Limpiándose la nariz con el dorso de la mano, se apoya contra una vieja máquina de refrescos."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:395
translate spanish hwb_s13_5eb9993d:

    # Trucker "Why yes, actually. Yes it is."
    Trucker "Ну да, вобщем-то. Мой."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:397
translate spanish hwb_s13_368e8f23:

    # "He deepens his voice, letting the tone sway up and down."
    "Profundiza su voz, dejando que el tono suba y baje."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:399
translate spanish hwb_s13_bf3d14f0:

    # "I can’t tell if he’s trying to be cool, seductive, charming, or just has a case of vertigo."
    "No sé si está tratando de parecer cool, seductor, encantador, o si solo tiene un caso de vértigo."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:401
translate spanish hwb_s13_4ea1a69c:

    # "Either way, I don’t think it has quite the effect he’s going for."
    "De cualquier manera, no creo que tenga el efecto que busca."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:403
translate spanish hwb_s13_34fb4da7:

    # Trucker "Well, tech-i-nactually, the trailer belongs to the company I work for."
    Trucker "Ну, технически, прицеп принадлежит компании, на которую я пахаю."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:405
translate spanish hwb_s13_e7a73834:

    # Trucker "But the truck? That zero to sixty miles an hour in ten seconds? That’s all me, sweetheart."
    Trucker "Но сам грузовик? Разгоняющийся от нуля до шестидесяти миль в час за десять секунд? Это все мое, детка."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:407
translate spanish hwb_s13_96261b21:

    # "He looks me straight in the eyes, emphasizing sweetheart, and I struggle to keep down the bile climbing up my throat."
    "Me mira directamente a los ojos, enfatizando \"cariño\", y lucho por contener la bilis que sube por mi garganta."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:411
translate spanish hwb_s13_6b9dc05f:

    # Amber "Oh, that’s nice. It’s very, uh…"
    Amber "Ох, здорово. Это очень, эм…"

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:413
translate spanish hwb_s13_6d3b9180:

    # "I try to think of a compliment, something that will take the conversation somewhere else. Anywhere but there."
    "Intento pensar en un cumplido, algo que lleve la conversación a otro lado. A cualquier lado menos allí."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:417
translate spanish hwb_s13_aea8ea15:

    # Amber "It’s very red."
    Amber "Он очень красный."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:419
translate spanish hwb_s13_71126069:

    # "Nailed it."
    "Lo logré."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:423
translate spanish hwb_s13_bfacd06e:

    # Trucker "Red on the outside, sure. But I promise you, that interior is pure white."
    Trucker "Ага, красный снаружи. Но уверяю тебя, интерьер полностью белый."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:425
translate spanish hwb_s13_2593db75:

    # "He winks."
    "Guiña un ojo."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:429
translate spanish hwb_s13_35532af3:

    # "If not for Marina, I would have driven off screaming into the night by now. I’m going to have to take a shower once we get to the Arches."
    "Si no fuera por Marina, ya me habría ido conduciendo y gritando en la noche. Voy a tener que ducharme cuando lleguemos a los Arcos."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:433
translate spanish hwb_s13_3ff25a91:

    # Trucker "In fact."
    Trucker "На самом деле."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:437
translate spanish hwb_s13_21780ffd:

    # "He isn’t stopping? Why isn’t he stopping?"
    "¿No va a parar? ¿Por qué no para?"

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:439
translate spanish hwb_s13_0a2c5936:

    # Trucker "Maybe you and your little friend wanna see why they call it my…"
    Trucker "Может быть ты и твоя маленькая подружка хотите посмотреть, почему его называют моим..."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:441
translate spanish hwb_s13_1020a302:

    # "He slams his elbow against the soda machine. Nothing happens."
    "Golpea con el codo la máquina de refrescos. No pasa nada."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:443
translate spanish hwb_s13_a5510c14:

    # "Cursing under his breath, he does it again with more force. This time, a can tumbles down, the momentum sending it rolling out the cache and across the asphalt."
    "Maldiciendo en voz baja, lo hace de nuevo con más fuerza. Esta vez, una lata cae, el impulso la hace rodar fuera del compartimento y cruzar el asfalto."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:449
translate spanish hwb_s13_a9855551:

    # Trucker "Pickup truck?"
    Trucker "... Грузовиком?"

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:458
translate spanish hwb_s13_97be58c9:

    # Amber "Marina! Are you almost done?"
    Amber "Марина! Ты все?"

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:460
translate spanish hwb_s13_21b47cf3:

    # Marina "ALMOST!"
    Marina "ПОЧТИ!"

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:462
translate spanish hwb_s13_9ffb5eaf:

    # "You were right about rest stops, Gramps. Why didn’t I listen?"
    "Tenías razón sobre las paradas de descanso, Abuelo. ¿Por qué no te hice caso?"

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:466
translate spanish hwb_s13_56bf8764:

    # Trucker "So how about it?"
    Trucker "Ну так че?"

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:468
translate spanish hwb_s13_a177d4f2:

    # "Presented with the option to feign ignorance or bash his head against the wall, I choose to feign ignorance, but only by a smidge."
    "Ante la opción de fingir ignorancia o estrellar su cabeza contra la pared, elijo fingir ignorancia, pero solo por un pelo."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:470
translate spanish hwb_s13_98883010:

    # "For Marina’s sake."
    "Por el bien de Marina."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:474
translate spanish hwb_s13_81f5a278:

    # Amber "Golly, Mister. We really appreciate the offer, but we already have a set of wheels."
    Amber "Черт возьми, мистер. Мы очень ценим это предложение, но у нас уже есть тачка."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:476
translate spanish hwb_s13_8174521d:

    # "Please let that work."
    "Por favor, que funcione."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:480
translate spanish hwb_s13_5f435a32:

    # Trucker "Ah, I understand."
    Trucker "А, понимаю."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:484
translate spanish hwb_s13_805d6321:

    # "Thank god."
    "Gracias a Dios."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:486
translate spanish hwb_s13_4dfe0b9b:

    # "The trucker sighs and wipes the sweat from his brow."
    "El camionero suspira y se seca el sudor de la frente."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:488
translate spanish hwb_s13_ff212036:

    # Trucker "‘Sides, I’m pretty busy, as is. After I finish this run, I’ma’ find myself some treasure."
    Trucker "Ну так то я и сам занятой. После того как я закончу этот рейс, я попру за сокровищами."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:490
translate spanish hwb_s13_9d8a2c49:

    # "Oh no."
    "Oh no."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:494
translate spanish hwb_s13_cdb09118:

    # Amber "Treasure?"
    Amber "Сокровищами?"

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:496
translate spanish hwb_s13_e71f3989:

    # Trucker "Yeah, y’know, that gold that miner left lying around. It’s all over the radio."
    Trucker "Ну да. Ну знаешь, золото, которое этот старатель тут всюду позакапывал. Это же на всех радиостанциях передают."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:500
translate spanish hwb_s13_ea1d9e67:

    # Amber "I may have heard a thing or two about it."
    Amber "Возможно и слышала что-то об этом."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:502
translate spanish hwb_s13_50a6b220:

    # "Great, another weirdo looking for the treasure. Just what we needed."
    "Genial, otro bicho raro buscando el tesoro. Justo lo que necesitábamos."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:504
translate spanish hwb_s13_8c7a05d3:

    # Trucker "It’s on my route, so I figured why not."
    Trucker "Мне по пути, так что я подумал, - “Че бы и нет?”."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:509
translate spanish hwb_s13_682057ba:

    # "Marina prances out of the restroom, restored to her old self."
    "Marina sale saltando del baño, recuperada como siempre."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:511
translate spanish hwb_s13_1f770b41:

    # Marina "All done! You two have a nice chat?"
    Marina "Готово! Вы вдвоем хорошо поболтали?"

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:513
translate spanish hwb_s13_28bcb6ca:

    # "I look at Marina, then the trucker, then to his truck."
    "Miro a Marina, luego al camionero, y luego a su camión."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:517
translate spanish hwb_s13_fb687434:

    # "Yet another despicable idea wiggles into my head. One that goes beyond picking on Mariah or leaving a tour."
    "Otra idea despreciable se me mete en la cabeza. Una que va más allá de molestar a Mariah o dejar un tour."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:519
translate spanish hwb_s13_474617d1:

    # Amber "Y’know, we had a really nice talk."
    Amber "Знаешь, мы действительно неплохо поболтали."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:521
translate spanish hwb_s13_154b7310:

    # Trucker "Really?"
    Trucker "Правда?"

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:523
translate spanish hwb_s13_7fc809f6:

    # "He says it like even he has trouble believing it."
    "Lo dice como si hasta él mismo tuviera problemas para creerlo."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:525
translate spanish hwb_s13_138bbd90:

    # Amber "Sure did!"
    Amber "Конечно!"

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:527
translate spanish hwb_s13_d6aedddc:

    # Amber "In fact, I have to go check on something in the R.V. real quick. Why don’t you take up where I left off and talk with good ol’—"
    Amber "На самом деле, мне надо сходить и кое-что проверить в трейлере. Почему бы тебе не продолжить там, где мы остановились в разговоре со старым добрым..."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:531
translate spanish hwb_s13_8f9a38d1:

    # Amber "What’s your name?"
    Amber "Как тебя зовут?"

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:535
translate spanish hwb_s13_da1fc28a:

    # Trucker "The boys on the road call me Jumbo."
    Trucker "Парни на дороге зовут меня Джамбо."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:541
translate spanish hwb_s13_399650a5:

    # Amber "Jumbo? Like the elepha—"
    Amber "Джамбо? Как сло—"

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:545
translate spanish hwb_s13_570ddba5:

    # Amber "Oh god."
    Amber "О, боже."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:552
translate spanish hwb_s13_31fb8f6f:

    # "To Marina’s terror, he bares his greasy smile."
    "Para el terror de Marina, muestra su sonrisa grasienta."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:557
translate spanish hwb_s13_e7bae504:

    # "She backs away and half-shields herself behind me, her voice softening to a whimper."
    "Ella retrocede y se protege a medias detrás de mí, su voz se suaviza hasta convertirse en un gemido."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:559
translate spanish hwb_s13_14c2985a:

    # Marina "Amber, I don’t think I want to talk to this guy."
    Marina "Эмбер, я не думаю, что я хочу говорить с ним."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:563
translate spanish hwb_s13_c6ca2c67:

    # "I block my lips with my hand, lowering my voice to a whisper."
    "Me tapo los labios con la mano, bajando la voz a un susurro."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:565
translate spanish hwb_s13_3a7d5e31:

    # Amber "I know, but just try to keep him distracted. I won’t be long."
    Amber "Знаю. Просто отвлеки его. Это ненадолго."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:569
translate spanish hwb_s13_031f03a4:

    # Amber "I’ll be right back, you two!"
    Amber "Я сейчас вернусь!"

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:574
translate spanish hwb_s13_829b7de0:

    # "Playing up the act, I skip across the lot and back to the motorhome."
    "Exagerando el acto, cruzo el estacionamiento saltando y vuelvo a la casa rodante."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:576
translate spanish hwb_s13_a51cc860:

    # Marina "Wait! Amber!"
    Marina "Стой! Эмбер!"

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:578
translate spanish hwb_s13_d085b505:

    # "I fight back the invisible tears."
    "Contengo las lágrimas invisibles."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:580
translate spanish hwb_s13_e0c58b84:

    # "Your sacrifice is for the greater good, Marina. It won’t be in vain."
    "Tu sacrificio es por el bien mayor, Marina. No será en vano."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:615
translate spanish hwb_s13_820264b5:

    # "I swing open the R.V.’s door and rush to the nearest drawer, rummaging through until I find what I need."
    "Abro la puerta de la casa rodante y corro al cajón más cercano, revolviendo hasta encontrar lo que necesito."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:617
translate spanish hwb_s13_0609969f:

    # "Screwdriver. Perfect."
    "Destornillador. Perfecto."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:656
translate spanish hwb_s13_8b65b0ef:

    # "Exiting the motorhome, I sneak over to the big rig, tiptoeing so I’m not spotted."
    "Al salir de la casa rodante, me escabullo hacia el camión grande, caminando de puntillas para no ser vista."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:658
translate spanish hwb_s13_3cfffd40:

    # "The driver’s side provides sufficient cover, hiding me from the trucker and Marina."
    "El lado del conductor proporciona suficiente cobertura, ocultándome del camionero y Marina."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:660
translate spanish hwb_s13_1e99f62f:

    # "I bend down and take a knee on the gravely concrete. With the screwdriver in hand, I unscrew the tire’s valve stem. Once it’s off, I take the screwdriver and insert it into the hole. The air seeps out with a steady hiss as the tire withers."
    "Me agacho y me arrodillo en el concreto con gravilla. Con el destornillador en mano, desenrosco la válvula de la llanta. Una vez que está fuera, tomo el destornillador y lo inserto en el agujero. El aire se escapa con un silbido constante mientras la llanta se desinfla."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:662
translate spanish hwb_s13_57c63355:

    # "‘Jumbo’ and Marina’s conversation carries across the lot. Even from here, I can almost feel the spit spray from his mouth as he tries chatting up Marina, with the exact same tactics he used on me."
    "La conversación entre 'Jumbo' y Marina cruza el estacionamiento. Incluso desde aquí, casi puedo sentir el salpicar de su saliva mientras intenta coquetear con Marina, usando exactamente las mismas tácticas que usó conmigo."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:664
translate spanish hwb_s13_3c5221bf:

    # Trucker "There is one kink that there truck has, though."
    Trucker ".. но у этого грузовика есть одна особенность."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:666
translate spanish hwb_s13_70bbee76:

    # "He pauses. I cringe, bracing for the incoming punchline."
    "Él hace una pausa. Me estremezco, preparándome para el remate que viene."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:668
translate spanish hwb_s13_56606668:

    # Trucker "It has a lot of {w=0.5}{i}thrust{/i}{w=0.5} to it when I use the brakes."
    Trucker "У него огромная {w=0.5}{i}тяга{/i}{w=0.5} когда я бью по тормозам."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:670
translate spanish hwb_s13_2ac5581d:

    # "Marina manages to squeeze out a stifled laugh, though it sounds more like uncontrollable sobbing."
    "Marina logra soltar una risa ahogada, aunque suena más como un sollozo incontrolable."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:672
translate spanish hwb_s13_2e32958e:

    # "Jumbo does the same, unleashing his crusty laugh upon the earth. It sounds like he might hack up an ashtray."
    "Jumbo hace lo mismo, desatando su risa áspera sobre la tierra. Suena como si fuera a escupir un cenicero."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:674
translate spanish hwb_s13_4e53012d:

    # "Keep the screaming inside, Amber. Resist the urge to repeatedly run him over with the motorhome."
    "Mantén los gritos dentro, Amber. Resiste la tentación de atropellarlo repetidas veces con la casa rodante."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:676
translate spanish hwb_s13_ebc0a852:

    # "I scurry from tire to tire, deflating them until my mission has been accomplished."
    "Corro de llanta en llanta, desinflándolas hasta completar mi misión."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:689
translate spanish hwb_s13_2b227f88:

    # "Sticking the loose caps in my back pocket, I emerge from the shadows and run back to Marina."
    "Meto las tapas sueltas en mi bolsillo trasero, salgo de las sombras y vuelvo corriendo hacia Marina."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:691
translate spanish hwb_s13_7e33dcbb:

    # "Just in time, too."
    "Justo a tiempo, además."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:693
translate spanish hwb_s13_7e2af2ea:

    # Trucker "Marina’s a pretty name. Sounds like it could bring flowin’ water and moisture to anywhere, even a barren wasteland like this."
    Trucker "Марина - такое милое имя. Звучит так, как будто оно может принести влажность куда угодно, даже на такую пустошь."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:695
translate spanish hwb_s13_bd8a6770:

    # Trucker "Y’know, I have a similar talen—"
    Trucker "Знаешь, а у меня есть похожий талан—"

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:700
translate spanish hwb_s13_31a8d154:

    # Amber "Alrighty, I’m back. Time to go, Marina."
    Amber "Океюшки, я вернулась. Пора ехать, Марина."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:706
translate spanish hwb_s13_9a1b59fe:

    # "I grab her shoulders and push her away from the trucker. My sole focus now is getting us out of here."
    "Le agarro los hombros y la aparto del camionero. Mi único enfoque ahora es sacarnos de aquí."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:708
translate spanish hwb_s13_2062bf7f:

    # Trucker "Aww, but we was havin’ so much fun."
    Trucker "Ээээ, но мы тут веселились."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:712
translate spanish hwb_s13_ba5d644f:

    # "A cold chill shoots up my spine, causing the hairs on the back of my neck to stick up. We walk faster."
    "Un escalofrío frío me sube por la espalda, erizando los vellos de la nuca. Caminamos más rápido."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:722
translate spanish hwb_s13_90f4358a:

    # Amber "I’m sorry, Mr. Jumbo, but we’re in a bit of a rush, too. We appreciate the conversation, though. Ain’t that right, Marina?"
    Amber "Извините, мистер Джамбо, но мы тоже спешим. Мы благодарны за такую беседу. Правда, Марина?"

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:724
translate spanish hwb_s13_9a94f15d:

    # "She swings her head back and forth, mouthing ‘no’ over and over."
    "Ella mueve la cabeza de un lado a otro, diciendo 'no' una y otra vez con los labios."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:726
translate spanish hwb_s13_68b538b0:

    # Trucker "Well, maybe we’ll meet down the road sometime."
    Trucker "Ну ладно, может на дороге встретимся как-нибудь."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:733
translate spanish hwb_s13_a2539030:

    # Trucker "Then we can have even more fun."
    Trucker "Тогда мы сможем повеселиться еще лучше."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:739
translate spanish hwb_s13_18dfc56b:

    # "He starts laughing again. Our feet move even faster than before. His laughter echos across the lot and bouncing off the nearby hills, growing louder until it becomes all I can hear."
    "Él se vuelve a reír. Nuestros pies se mueven aún más rápido que antes. Su risa resuena por el estacionamiento y rebota en las colinas cercanas, haciéndose más fuerte hasta que es lo único que escucho."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:741
translate spanish hwb_s13_6848eebc:

    # Amber "Run. Don’t look back. Just run."
    Amber "Беги. Не оглядывайся. Просто беги!"

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:743
translate spanish hwb_s13_6762d9a4:

    # Marina "I’m trying, Amber!"
    Marina "Я пытаюсь, Эмбер!"

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:745
translate spanish hwb_s13_dbd5dfac:

    # "I push her harder. Our feet finally pick up enough momentum and we scramble for the motorhome, the cackling now sounding closer than ever."
    "La empujo con más fuerza. Nuestros pies finalmente toman suficiente impulso y corremos hacia la casa rodante, con la risa sonando más cerca que nunca."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:747
translate spanish hwb_s13_4370d1f4:

    # "Marina reaches the RV first and leaps inside, immediately twisting to lock her door."
    "Marina llega primero a la RV y salta adentro, girándose de inmediato para cerrar su puerta con llave."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:789
translate spanish hwb_s13_d799696a:

    # "I jump in next, without bothering to clip in my seatbelt or even check the rear."
    "Yo salto detrás, sin molestarme en abrocharme el cinturón o siquiera revisar atrás."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:793
translate spanish hwb_s13_3d33456f:

    # "The engine roars to life and I slam on the gas pedal, leaving a plume of exhaust behind as we screech onto the road."
    "El motor ruge y piso el acelerador a fondo, dejando una nube de escape mientras salimos chirriando hacia la carretera."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:797
translate spanish hwb_s13_d33be656:

    # "When I’m sure we’re safe, I let out the biggest sigh of my life."
    "Cuando estoy segura de que estamos a salvo, suelto el suspiro más grande de mi vida."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:799
translate spanish hwb_s13_a9e4e929:

    # "Gravity is lighter, the air conditioning is fresher. Life is a gift."
    "La gravedad es más ligera, el aire acondicionado es más fresco. La vida es un regalo."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:801
translate spanish hwb_s13_063254d3:

    # "A hard force repeatedly hits my shoulder, shattering my zen-like appreciation of existence."
    "Una fuerza dura golpea mi hombro repetidamente, rompiendo mi apreciación zen de la existencia."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:805
translate spanish hwb_s13_e875b7ec:

    # Marina "Stop. {w=0.4} Leaving. {w=0.4} Me. {w=0.4} With. {w=0.4} Weirdos."
    Marina "Прекрати. {w=0.4} Оставлять. {w=0.4} Меня. {w=0.4} С. {w=0.4} Чудаками."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:807
translate spanish hwb_s13_d0c21bc9:

    # "Marina swings one last punch. This one hits the hardest."
    "Marina lanza un último golpe. Este duele más."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:809
translate spanish hwb_s13_fec0a263:

    # Marina "Jerk!" with hpunch
    Marina "Тупица!" with hpunch

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:811
translate spanish hwb_s13_1509795b:

    # Amber "Sheesh, that hurts."
    Amber "Эй, больно же."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:813
translate spanish hwb_s13_5557783f:

    # Marina "Good!"
    Marina "Хорошо!"

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:817
translate spanish hwb_s13_23ba877d:

    # Amber "I might deserve it. Just a little, though."
    Amber "Может я и заслужила это. Совсем чуть-чуть."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:821
translate spanish hwb_s13_1055a340:

    # Marina "You think?"
    Marina "Думаешь?"

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:825
translate spanish hwb_s13_1c13b9a7:

    # "I rub my shoulder, trying to soothe the throbbing. She packs a surprisingly hard punch for such a tiny girl."
    "Me froto el hombro, tratando de calmar el dolor. Da un puñetazo sorprendentemente fuerte para ser una chica tan pequeña."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:829
translate spanish hwb_s13_cbf9d99a:

    # "Marina flings herself back into her seat and pouts."
    "Marina se deja caer de nuevo en su asiento y hace un puchero."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:833
translate spanish hwb_s13_b58568ad:

    # Marina "Why did you even leave, anyway?"
    Marina "Почему ты вообще оставила меня?"

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:837
translate spanish hwb_s13_58e4aa30:

    # Amber "He said he was after the treasure, so I decided to conduct some secret ops."
    Amber "Он сказал, что едет за сокровищами. Так что я решила провести небольшую спецоперацию."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:839
translate spanish hwb_s13_151a311a:

    # "Grinning, I dig into my back pocket and pull out the caps. It takes a few seconds for Marina to register what I’ve done, but once she does, she joins me with a goofy grin of her own."
    "Sonriendo, meto la mano en mi bolsillo trasero y saco las tapas. A Marina le toma unos segundos darse cuenta de lo que hice, pero una vez que lo hace, se une a mí con una sonrisa tonta propia."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:843
translate spanish hwb_s13_55e69834:

    # Marina "You’re so sneaky, Amber."
    Marina "Ну ты и хитрюга, Эмбер."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:845
translate spanish hwb_s13_3c7fc5d5:

    # "I toss the caps out the window and take a sip of my coffee. It’s cold now, but drinking it has never felt more satisfying."
    "Tiro las tapas por la ventana y tomo un sorbo de mi café. Ahora está frío, pero beberlo nunca se ha sentido más satisfactorio."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:849
translate spanish hwb_s13_c6e3fa2d:

    # Marina "But Amber."
    Marina "Но Эмбер..."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:853
translate spanish hwb_s13_e23d32e8:

    # Amber "Hm?"
    Amber "М?"

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:859
translate spanish hwb_s13_27f4a40e:

    # Marina "Can we never go to a rest stop again?"
    Marina "Давай больше никогда не будем заезжать в придорожные места для отдыха?"

translate spanish strings:

    # game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:2
    old "Trucker"
    new "Дальнобойщик"

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:213
translate spanish hwb_s13_a044e7a6:

    # "The lonely island is lit only by the sharp, unnatural light emanating from a shack on the edge of the lot, never treading more than a short distance from the building, denying its surroundings even the comfort of a dim glow."
    "La isla solitaria está iluminada solo por la luz aguda y antinatural que emana de una choza en el borde del lote, sin alejarse nunca más de una corta distancia del edificio, negando a sus alrededores incluso el consuelo de un resplandor tenue."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:86
translate spanish hwb_s13_5bf0513d:

    # "My voice grows tense—urgent, my driving sloppy. Every pore of my clammy palms is stuck to the wheel. The hollowness comes back."
    "Mi voz se vuelve tensa, urgente, mi conducción descuidada. Cada poro de mis palmas sudorosas está pegado al volante. El vacío regresa."

# game/script/hwb_s13.rpy:213
translate spanish hwb_s13_d43422f5:

    # "The lonely island is lit by a sharp light emanating from a shack on the edge of the lot. It brightens up the immediate area, and the surrounding terrain falls off into a dim glow."
    "La isla solitaria está iluminada por una luz aguda que emana de una choza en el borde del lote. Ilumina el área inmediata, y el terreno circundante se desvanece en un resplandor tenue."

translate spanish strings:

    # script/hwb_s13.rpy:48
    old "Driving to Arches"
    new "Driving to Arches"

